    <item>
      <title>沙特化妆品零售商 Nice One 宣布 3.2 亿美元 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/saudi-cosmetics-retailer-nice-one-announces-320-million-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯在线化妆品零售商 Nice One Beauty 计划通过在利雅得进行首次公开​​募股 (IPO) 筹集高达 12.1 亿里亚尔（3.22 亿美元），这将为今年沙特阿拉伯的一系列上市活动再添新成员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/saudi-cosmetics-retailer-nice-one-announces-320-million-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 06:03:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳门 11 月博彩收入增长 14.9%，超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/macau-gaming-revenue-rises-14-9-in-november-exceeds-estimate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[11 月份，澳门博彩收入增长 14.9%，超出了分析师的预期，而由于缺乏假期，11 月份的博彩收入通常较为低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/macau-gaming-revenue-rises-14-9-in-november-exceeds-estimate</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 05:17:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
